MA(2)

length = 10000
noise = rnorm(length)
ma2 = NULL
for (i in 3:length) {
  ma2[i] = noise[i] + 0.7 * noise[i-1] + 0.2 * noise[i-2]
}
ma2.process = ts(ma2[3:length])
plot(ma2.process)

acf(ma2.process)
